summary:
A patch to the mod \"All barrels are searchable\" that makes searchable barrels breakable and  have physics(Think how a tankard roll\'s around on the ground) yet barrels do not .Now they do along with breaking .

Not beta or Alpha At this point However see warnings
descriptionHtml:
A patch to the mod \"All barrels are searchable\" that makes searchable barrels breakable and  have physics(Think how a tankard roll\'s around on the ground) yet barrels do not .Now they do along with breaking .

They are heavy but do move and break. They do not go flying around when bumped into .
************************************************************************************************************************************************
The screen shots will be in before and after 
***********************************************************************************************************************************************
barrels once broken MAY OR MAY NOT RESPAWN I Do Not Know yet if someone can confirm this for me i would be grateful.

WARNING:if a barrel is destroyed with items in it they are lost . later plan to make it to were they are dropped for most common items as the debris also have plans to make burnt destroyed or not 


Well i am at a loss for the idea on how to make them reappear with out a timed script any one got any idea\'s?
Required mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10110
author: Hollow_Fang

files.name: Breakable Physic Searchable Barrels
files.changelogHtml:
Made the large Puff on destrution to small
Made almost All barrels Working and breakable (still have not done snowy barrels or light light brown barrels)
made wood drop out place holder for wood splinters
changed weight of some of the barrels so they are not super light and go flying under light push yet will still move when hit or pushed with enough force (ie. FUS'RO DAH)
Now Stable - Still unknown if broken barrel will respawn
